  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="Aink239-kilavi">varaiviṭai vaittup pirival eṉṟa talaimakaṟkut tōḻi kūṟiyatu.  </p>
        <p xml:lang="en"> What the confidante told the hero who said, “I will leave, having placed a gap in the marriage.”
          
        </p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink239">
<l>curumpuṇak kaḷitta pukarmuka vēḻa</l>
<l>mirumpiṇart tuṟukaṟ piṭicettut taḻūuniṉ</l>
<l>kuṉṟukeḻu naṉṉāṭṭuc ceṉṟa piṉṟai</l>
<l>nēriṟaip paṇaittōṇ ñekiḻa</l>
<l>vārā yāyiṉ vāḻēn teyyō</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
        <l>After you had gone to your good country with hills,</l>
        <l>where the spotted-faced bull elephant which was in rut,</l>
        <l rend="indent3">so that bees feed [on its musth],</l>
        <l>embraced a dark, rough boulder, thinking it to be a she-elephant—</l>
        <l rend="space">if you do not come back,</l>
        <l>so that her bamboo-like arms with fine joints grow emaciated,</l>
        <l>we would not live — alas!</l>
        
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
